description:
Compress, Encrypt, Exchange and Backup your data. Fastest archiver with support for ZIP, ZIPX, 7Z, PA, RAR, ISO (over 60+ formats), strongest compression and secure 256-bit AES encryption!
	
### Notes

* This package uses PowerArchiver 2016 MSI installer extracted from PowerArchiver's .exe file. There's no way to omit extracting window, if you use self-extracting exe, so I use extracted msi package instead.
author: ConeXware,  Inc.
